- id: '2069836260433350723'
  text: 'The math on a bad proposal process:


    → No discovery = writing into a vacuum


    → Generic structure = client feels like proposal #7 in your outbox


    → One price = a yes/no decision at the hardest possible moment


    → No follow-up = the deal goes to whoever showed up again'
