- id: '2069857362618290283'
  text: "No worries sorry for any confusion, I think some issues will be algo has\
    \ been pushing new tracks over older tracks and newer artists out on these radio,\
    \ TV streams and playlists. Which is kinda the wrong approach because we leave\
    \ our long term artists behind but kinda my fault as I broke the algo with Claude\
    \ and didn't even notice till we got an influx of traffic and saw what was being\
    \ pushed out \U0001F602 \n\nEither way thanks for bringing it up. Because I think\
    \ I need to make more incentives to have people like a track and follow artists.\
    \ The buttons are so hidden and small it could be my fault on the design.\n\n\
    Any drastic changes tho I would get in touch. By design the algo tries to push\
    \ evenly on new uploads but that will change as can't leave too many older tracks\
    \ behind."
